    "description_long": "This is a large, boxy fire truck with a predominantly red exterior, featuring white and yellow accent markings along its sides. The vehicle has a cab at the front for the driver and crew, with windows and side mirrors visible. Along the sides, there are multiple compartments likely used for storing firefighting equipment, as well as visible wheels and a ladder mounted on the roof. Emergency lights are mounted on the roof and front, and there are hose connections and outlets on the side panels. The truck's robust build and detailed features suggest it is designed for rapid response and heavy-duty firefighting tasks in urban environments.",
